* Perform a routing of a source to an MNA-420 decoder and wait long enough so that this is applied.
* Then stop NMS, reboot the MNA-420 decoder and restart NMS again.
* Now check (after sufficient time to allow NMS to startup completely) that the same routing is again applied to the MNA-420 decoder.

