Create new v0 APIs for creating, updating and deleting imported sources which will be called from intersite-resource-sharing-service.

These APIs should not be called from anywhere other than resource sharing service. Other clients should be blocked.


===================================================================================
DOD:


Reference : [OCS Arch - Source Sharing - vGEAX - Confluence|https://barco-nv.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/GEAX/pages/844759042/OCS+Arch+-+Source+Sharing]

!image-20260205-043520.png|width=648,alt="image-20260205-043520.png"!

* Get alignment on API specs
* The APIs should not be accessible from outside the system. 

=> {{The endpoint should not be added into Guardian, should also not match the regex present there. The ticket states only from resource sharing but disallowing from outside should be enough, other services are internal at the end.}}

=> {{Resource sharing has the resposibility of removing the unwanted details (like device info) from source details.}}

=> {{Resource sharing will do FQDN validation (if required)}}

h1. Creation of imported sources

Endpoint: *POST* {{/api/configure/v0/imported-sources}}


Body:

{noformat}{
    ...CreateBarcoDto,
    importedSource: {   [Required]
        id: "string",
        siteInfo : {
            fqdn: "string",
            name: "string"
        }
    }
}{noformat}


Response:

{noformat}{
    ...barcoSource,
    importedSource: {
        id: "string",
        siteInfo : {
            fqdn: "string",
            name: "string"
        }
    }
}{noformat}

h1. Updating imported sources

Endpoint: *PATCH* {{/api/configure/v0/imported-sources:id}}

Body:

{noformat}{
    ...PatchBarcoDto,
    importedSource: {   [Required]
        id: "string",
        siteInfo : {
            fqdn: "string",
            name: "string"
        }
    }
}{noformat}



Response:

{noformat}{
    ...barcoSource,
    importedSource: {
        id: "string",
        siteInfo : {
            fqdn: "string",
            name: "string"
        }
    }
}{noformat}

h1. Deleting imported sources

Endpoint: *DELETE* {{/api/configure/v0/imported-sources:id}}

Only delete the source if it is an imported source.

